common.enums

Enum ShimKey

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ShimKey>
      • common.enums.ShimKey
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ShimKey>

    public enum ShimKey
extends java.lang.Enum<ShimKey>
    Contains all Shimmer supported shimkeys. Also contains all the data types supported by each shimkey. In turn each Data type contains what version it is supported by. The shim key can be set within the config properties file, and should then be loaded from there.
    See Also:
    DataType, PropertiesLoad
